{% comment %} ===== GENERAL INTEGRATION TIPS ===== {% endcomment %}

{% comment %}
  PLACEMENT GUIDELINES:
  
  1. BEST LOCATIONS:
     - After product price
     - Before quantity selector
     - Before add to cart button
     - In product form area
  
  2. AVOID PLACING:
     - Inside form tags (bundle has its own cart logic)
     - In variant selector areas
     - In product image galleries
     - In header/footer areas
  
  3. CONDITIONAL RENDERING:
     - Only show on specific products
     - Hide on certain device types
     - Show based on inventory levels
  
  EXAMPLE CONDITIONS:
  
  <!-- Only show for specific product -->
  {% if product.handle == 'your-product-handle' %}
    {% render 'driftmats-bundle', product: product %}
  {% endif %}
  
  <!-- Only show for products in specific collection -->
  {% assign bundle_products = collections['bundle-eligible'] %}
  {% if bundle_products.products contains product %}
    {% render 'driftmats-bundle', product: product %}
  {% endif %}
  
  <!-- Only show if product has inventory -->
  {% if product.available %}
    {% render 'driftmats-bundle', product: product %}
  {% endif %}
  
  <!-- Hide on mobile devices -->
  <div class="hidden-mobile">
    {% render 'driftmats-bundle', product: product %}
  </div>
{% endcomment %}